Echo '###'
Echo '### Pascal is no longer part of the MPW environment because the'
Echo '###   Pascal Libraries are not compatible with new SC based MPW CLibraries.'
ECho '###   To prevent the inadvertent use of these incompatible libraries'
Echo '###   the Pascal tool and the related PasMat and PasRef tools have'
Echo '###   been placed in the MPW Archive, and this explanation has been provided.'
Echo '### With appropriate care, you can use the archived Pascal with MPW.  See'
Echo '###   the "MPW Archive Read Me" for more information.'  
Echo '### This script can be safely deleted at any time.  '
Echo '###' 
Exit 1
